.be/informatie-voor-de-technicus-voor-brandbeveiligingsapparatuur\">More info on the obligations for recognised technicians for fire protection equipment.</a></p><p>The <strong>company </strong>for which the technician works must also have an <a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-bedrijven-voor-brandbeveiligingsapparatuur\">approval as a company for</a> fire protection equipment.</p><ul></ul>",
